Goal
Update the Enterprise Architecture Waivers object/record experience per the TD working group analysis by:

Converting some existing fields (datatype / usage change as defined in analysis)

Removing deprecated fields

Adding new fields required by the analysis

Context / Reference
Details and the field-by-field decisions are documented here:
https://wiki.usaa.com/x/mdcknQ

Scope (What will be changed)

Implement the field changes exactly as documented in the wiki (convert/remove/add).

Update any impacted page layouts / record pages / flows / validation rules / automation / reports that reference these fields.

Ensure the updated fields are available with correct FLS/permissions for intended users.

Target environment: Production (deploy via standard release process).


All field add / convert / remove changes are implemented exactly per the wiki.

Record pages/layouts updated: new fields shown, removed fields not visible anywhere.

No broken dependencies (flows, validations, reports, automation, integrations).

FLS/permission sets updated for intended users.

Basic validation completed in Production-ready package
